</script><div style="margin-top:.5rem;font-size:.78rem;color:#888;text-align:center">Location and service area</div></div></section><footer style="background:#0F172A;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);padding:3rem 1.5rem 1.5rem"><div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center"><p style="margin:1.5rem 0 0;font-size:.82rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)">Sunshine Coast, Australia · <a href="mailto:contact@geotechnicalengineering1.xyz" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)">contact@geotechnicalengineering1.xyz</a> · © 2026</p></div><div data-updated="2026-04-12" style="font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-top:.8rem">Last updated: 2026-04-12</div><div data-authority-refs class="authority-refs" style="text-align:center;font-size:.8rem;padding:.5rem 0;opacity:.6"><strong>References:</strong>ASTM Standards · USACE Engineer Manuals · ISO Geotechnical</div></footer><script>(function(){
